title: t.A.T.u
description:
This is a complete and entire discography of the group t.A.T.u. This includes all of the songs that they have released publicly in albums. I have scoured the internet for other discographies on this group and found them to be a large unorganized mess of files with incoherent names and extra fluff thrown in. From those I organized this batch of music into this torrent in order to share it with all of you out there. I pruned and picked out duplicate songs in this batch that appear in the different t.A.T.u. albums. So there is no 2 songs here that are exactly the same.

THERE ARE NO DUPLICATE SONGS.

All of these are in .mp3 format.
